ygData.messageBody:
Jaezebel,

Were you ever successful? I have a half-elf on Tarrew Marr who's at level 9
wearing patch and her butt is still hanging out for all of Norrath to see.

I'm happy to announce that I've been finally able to put on some patch, and
now Wynsong's bottom half is covered with the black leather look. The patch
tunic is actually skimpier (??!!) than her birthday suit, lol. However,
she's looking very cool and has some AC finally. :-) So, now I'm the cute
little redheaded Woodelf running around Rivervale sporting the black leather
biker bard from h*** look. ;-)

Safe travels,
Wynsong
Woodelf Bard, Level 4
Rivervale, Quellious
